Calculation: Sum of All Income Categories (DR and NDR)

Field Description: Very low income units non-deed restricted
Calculation:
IF CO_VLOW_INCOME_NDR > 0, 
THEN CO_VLOW_INCOME_NDR
ELSE IF BP_VLOW_INCOME_NDR
THEN BP_VLOW_INCOME_NDR
ELSE IF VLOW_INCOME_NDR > 0 
THEN VLOW_INCOME_NDR

Field Description: Very low income units deed restricted
Calculation:
IF CO_VLOW_INCOME_DR > 0, 
THEN CO_VLOW_INCOME 
ELSE IF BP_VLOW_INCOME_DR 
THEN BP_VLOW_INCOME_DR
ELSE IF VLOW_INCOME_DR > 0 
THEN VLOW_INCOME_DR

Field Description: Low income units non-deed restricted
Calculation: IF CO_LOW_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERM > 0, THEN CO_LOW_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERM ELSE IF BP_LOW_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERM THEN BP_LOW_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERMELSE IF LOW_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERMITS > 0 THEN LOW_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERMITS

Field Description: Low income units deed restricted
Calculation: IF CO_LOW_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERM > 0, THEN CO_LOW_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERM ELSE IF BP_LOW_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERM THEN BP_LOW_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERMELSE IF LOW_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERMITS > 0 THEN LOW_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERMITS

Field Description: Number of units for moderate income non-deed restricted
Calculation: IF CO_MOD_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERM > 0, THEN CO_MOD_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERM ELSE IF BP_MOD_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERM THEN BP_MOD_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERMELSE IF MOD_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERMITS > 0 THEN MOD_INCOME_NDR_CON_ENT_PERMITS

Field Description: Number of units for moderate income deed restricted
Calculation: IF CO_MOD_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERM > 0, THEN CO_MOD_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERM ELSE IF BP_MOD_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERM THEN BP_MOD_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERMELSE IF MOD_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERMITS > 0 THEN MOD_INCOME_DR_CON_ENT_PERMITS

Field Description: Above moderate income units
Calculation: IF CO_ABOVE_MOD_INCOME_CON_ENT_PERM > 0, THEN CO_ABOVE_MOD_INCOME_CON_ENT_PERM ELSE IF BP_ABOVE_MOD_INCOME_CON_ENT_PERM THEN BP_ABOVE_MOD_INCOME_CON_ENT_PERMELSE IF ABOVE_MOD_INCOME_CON_ENT_PERMITS > 0 THEN ABOVE_MOD_INCOME_CON_ENT_PERMITS
